{
  "texts": [
    "Given that the GMAT exam employs an adaptive testing format-wherein a test taker's performance on prior questions dictates the difficulty level of subsequent ones-we maintain that administering the tests through the official GMAT exam website constitutes the most authentic method for evaluating the performance of LLMs.",
    "This approach is likely to provide the most accurate estimation of the AI's proficiency and competency.",
    "By leveraging the official testing platform, we can ensure that the AI is subjected to the same dynamic adjustments in difficulty that human test-takers face, thereby offering a fair and rigorous assessment of its capabilities in a standardized context.",
    "Our choice of exams was strategic; to mitigate the potential influence of publicly available free practice exams on the results, we included premium practice exams among the three exam sets for each model.",
    "These premium exams were not publicly accessible, thereby ensuring a level of novelty and challenge for the LLMs."
  ]
}